WEBVTT

01:34.440 --> 01:37.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL OF THE SAME NAME
BY ZHU YI ON WWW.JJWXC.NET

01:37.800 --> 01:38.640
SNACKS OF HONG KONG, CHINA

01:38.720 --> 01:40.920
- Why have I never seen you before?
- I'm in the choreography department.

01:41.000 --> 01:41.520
NANWU

01:41.600 --> 01:42.800
- Are you from the art college?
- Yes, I am.

01:42.880 --> 01:45.320
- That's great.
- Well, thanks. What about you?

01:45.400 --> 01:47.280
- Are we in the same grade?
- Maybe.

01:47.360 --> 01:48.520
What's your major?

01:48.600 --> 01:50.280
Computer science.

01:51.200 --> 01:53.000
I'm going to the bathroom.
We'll talk later.

01:53.080 --> 01:55.120
- Turn right up ahead and right again.
- Thank you. Bye.

01:55.200 --> 01:56.400
See you later.

01:57.720 --> 01:58.640
Chen Junwen.

01:59.240 --> 02:00.400
What's up?

02:04.200 --> 02:06.280
Who was that girl just now?
Is she from our class?

02:06.360 --> 02:07.920
Why don't I remember there is
such a good-looking girl in my class?

02:08.000 --> 02:09.600
She's definitely not from our class.

02:09.680 --> 02:10.720
She was at the next table.

02:10.800 --> 02:12.600
She asked me where the bathroom was.

02:12.680 --> 02:15.360
I don't know why she asked me
instead of the waitress. Oh my God.

02:15.440 --> 02:16.280
I'm going to the bathroom.

02:16.360 --> 02:17.680
Sit down.

02:17.760 --> 02:18.600
What?

02:18.680 --> 02:20.480
Did you get over the pain
of being a backup so soon?

02:20.560 --> 02:23.000
Are we friends?
Why are you talking so harshly?

02:23.080 --> 02:24.320
Just shut up.

02:25.360 --> 02:27.560
It's been so many days since we graduated.
Have you found a job yet?

02:27.640 --> 02:29.080
It's hard.

02:29.160 --> 02:30.680
I heard

02:30.760 --> 02:32.080
that there are still a lot of graduates

02:32.160 --> 02:34.640
this year who haven't found a job.

02:34.720 --> 02:35.720
Scary?

02:36.400 --> 02:37.720
We're not like Sang Yan,

02:37.800 --> 02:40.680
who found a high-paying
and less stressful game design job

02:40.760 --> 02:41.920
in Nanwu right after graduation.

02:42.000 --> 02:43.720
It's not that I went to them,

02:43.800 --> 02:45.280
- but they came to me.
- That's right.

02:45.360 --> 02:46.800
Just like when you had a girlfriend.

02:46.880 --> 02:48.720
Many girls came to you
to confess their love to you,

02:49.640 --> 02:51.360
but I've never seen you say yes.

02:55.400 --> 02:59.840
YIHE

03:03.520 --> 03:05.680
Excuse me. Am I disturbing you?

03:05.760 --> 03:08.520
I'm a reporter for Yihe Daily.

03:09.360 --> 03:11.400
I just saw the book you were reading.

03:11.480 --> 03:13.120
You seem to be studying journalism.

03:16.200 --> 03:17.920
Our newspaper office is right next to it.

03:18.000 --> 03:19.560
I'm guessing

03:19.640 --> 03:21.240
you're studying
or just recently graduated, right?

03:22.240 --> 03:23.480
Recent graduate.

03:24.240 --> 03:25.200
That's great.

03:25.280 --> 03:27.520
I'm researching a topic right now.

03:27.600 --> 03:28.880
It's about why young people

03:28.960 --> 03:31.840
don't want to go back
to their hometowns to work.

03:32.760 --> 03:35.720
Would it be possible for me
to interview you about that?

03:40.640 --> 03:42.040
There must be a reason

03:42.120 --> 03:44.440
why they don't want to go home.

03:46.880 --> 03:49.480
Can you tell me more about that?

03:49.560 --> 03:50.800
For example,

03:51.440 --> 03:52.920
what are your reasons?

03:56.600 --> 03:58.920
Okay. Sorry to interrupt.

04:04.280 --> 04:06.600
YIHE DAILY. YE YUYANG. REPORTER

04:13.160 --> 04:15.920
ZHAO YUANDONG

04:21.959 --> 04:23.640
- Hello?
- Jiang.

04:24.160 --> 04:26.760
You graduated,
so you should come back to Nanwu.

04:26.840 --> 04:29.880
Mr. Zheng said
he'd treat you to dinner today.

04:29.960 --> 04:31.080
Thank him for me.

04:32.120 --> 04:33.400
I'll stay in Yihe.

04:34.720 --> 04:35.760
Why?

04:35.840 --> 04:37.600
I miss you.

04:38.120 --> 04:41.280
If you come back,
I can see you more often.

04:42.080 --> 04:43.280
Miss me?

04:45.680 --> 04:47.920
In my four years of college,
you came to me only once.

04:49.080 --> 04:51.120
And that was during your trip

04:51.200 --> 04:53.360
to Yihe with Zheng Kejia.

04:55.520 --> 04:57.680
I don't want to go back to Nanwu or Beiyu.

04:58.520 --> 04:59.560
Also,

05:00.280 --> 05:02.040
don't you know why I left?

05:20.600 --> 05:21.800
3,614 DAYS

05:31.400 --> 05:32.480
You're back.

05:38.080 --> 05:40.520
Why are you wet? Wait for me.

05:52.680 --> 05:54.080
You neither took an umbrella

05:54.840 --> 05:56.200
nor asked me to pick you up.

06:02.560 --> 06:04.080
It rained so suddenly.

06:04.160 --> 06:05.480
I was working.

06:07.680 --> 06:09.000
You've been so tired lately,

06:09.920 --> 06:11.440
so can you ask for a leave to rest?

06:18.520 --> 06:19.880
Don't worry.

06:19.960 --> 06:21.040
Let me do it.

06:22.880 --> 06:25.520
Can I go to Yihe soon?

06:30.560 --> 06:32.480
My sister won't be back
for summer vacation

06:32.560 --> 06:35.280
and says she's got a boyfriend.
He's quite old.

06:35.800 --> 06:38.040
My family is worried
and wants me to go there

06:38.120 --> 06:39.400
in case he's a liar.

06:44.720 --> 06:46.960
Or I can go sometime later.

06:47.560 --> 06:48.760
When?

06:50.360 --> 06:51.920
In a couple of days.

06:52.000 --> 06:54.240
If nothing happens, I'll come back early.

06:57.360 --> 06:59.200
It's good to visit Zhi.

07:00.400 --> 07:03.040
She's a little girl.
It's really unsettling.

07:03.120 --> 07:04.520
Don't argue with her.

07:07.360 --> 07:08.600
Shall I book a hotel for you?

07:09.200 --> 07:10.520
I know that place better than you.

07:14.800 --> 07:17.040
Take a shower now. Don't catch a cold.

07:18.480 --> 07:19.520
And…

07:21.120 --> 07:23.000
remember to bring an umbrella next time,

07:23.760 --> 07:24.880
but you'd better

07:25.720 --> 07:27.080
call me.

07:56.320 --> 07:57.440
Wen Shuangjiang.

08:01.560 --> 08:02.880
Do you have something on your mind?

08:06.160 --> 08:07.200
No.

08:32.679 --> 08:34.080
I said I'm fine.

08:37.760 --> 08:39.080
But I feel

08:40.600 --> 08:41.840
you're not concentrating at all.

08:42.880 --> 08:44.320
I'm just a bit tired.

08:46.800 --> 08:48.200
Then get some rest.

08:52.960 --> 08:54.720
If you don't pester me.

08:56.520 --> 08:57.440
Good night.

09:19.920 --> 09:22.760
No matter where you are, I'll find you.

09:38.160 --> 09:39.400
Wen Yifan.

09:41.680 --> 09:42.960
No matter what,

09:45.760 --> 09:46.720
I'll take you.

09:51.040 --> 09:53.720
Who can just take anything from me?

10:17.520 --> 10:18.920
It's so early.

10:19.000 --> 10:20.560
Check-in hasn't even started yet.

10:21.480 --> 10:22.600
Are you sleepy?

10:24.600 --> 10:25.800
I'll stay with you for a while.

10:25.880 --> 10:27.480
I'll leave as soon as check-in starts.

10:29.480 --> 10:31.320
I won't be gone long,

10:31.400 --> 10:33.880
but you insisted on coming with me.
Are you so sad to see me go?

10:36.800 --> 10:37.720
Of course.

10:48.280 --> 10:50.120
Looks like check-in has begun.

11:04.200 --> 11:05.960
I'll go through security
and get ready to board.

11:08.120 --> 11:09.960
Okay. Stay with me this far.

11:12.720 --> 11:13.880
Let me know when you get home.

11:14.400 --> 11:15.280
Be safe.

11:18.200 --> 11:19.280
I'll miss you.

11:21.000 --> 11:22.040
See you later.

12:12.560 --> 12:13.880
I'm home.

12:18.040 --> 12:19.240
This is…

12:21.560 --> 12:22.640
my home.

12:41.960 --> 12:43.400
This is my home.

14:13.760 --> 14:14.960
You little brat.

14:15.040 --> 14:18.400
I'll follow you anywhere. I will
go with you to the ends of the earth.

14:19.680 --> 14:23.280
If I left, Che Xingde
wouldn't have to harm you.

14:24.800 --> 14:25.840
Sang Yan.

14:26.360 --> 14:27.480
I'm sorry.

14:28.640 --> 14:29.760
I'm sorry.

14:32.320 --> 14:33.440
I'm sorry.

14:48.200 --> 14:49.400
I'm in Yihe.

14:49.480 --> 14:51.080
Call me if anything happens.

14:51.160 --> 14:52.280
I won't put it on mute.

14:56.200 --> 14:58.040
I really don't know why you came with me.

14:58.120 --> 15:00.360
Dian asked me instead of you
to feed the cat.

15:02.280 --> 15:03.360
Actually,

15:04.080 --> 15:05.520
I've decided to join Help Me,

15:05.600 --> 15:07.280
so I'm here to apprentice, okay?

15:08.200 --> 15:09.080
Sure.

15:15.800 --> 15:16.640
So much cat food.

15:17.320 --> 15:18.560
When will it be finished?

15:20.880 --> 15:21.960
Dian.

15:22.480 --> 15:23.360
Dian.

15:24.200 --> 15:25.160
Dian.

15:32.200 --> 15:33.160
Su Haoan.

15:36.320 --> 15:37.840
I feel a bit strange.

15:41.880 --> 15:43.040
You're amazing.

15:47.720 --> 15:48.760
Come here.

15:51.920 --> 15:54.840
She told me she's only away
for a day or two, but why is the closet

15:54.920 --> 15:56.360
and dresser empty?

15:57.720 --> 15:58.920
Hello.

15:59.000 --> 16:01.800
The user you're calling
is temporarily unavailable.

16:01.880 --> 16:03.720
What next? She doesn't seem to be online.

16:05.680 --> 16:06.800
I'll call Sang Yan.

16:11.080 --> 16:12.840
Stop the car.

16:16.240 --> 16:17.600
Airport. Hurry up.

16:28.240 --> 16:30.000
Su Haoan. Su Haoan.

16:31.280 --> 16:33.000
- She's not back yet?
- How come you're so fast?

16:33.080 --> 16:34.320
By air?

16:36.080 --> 16:38.240
I thought her room was too empty,

16:38.320 --> 16:40.600
and I was anxious, so I…

17:05.880 --> 17:07.560
Did she go back to her mom?

17:09.079 --> 17:10.160
No way.

17:45.480 --> 17:48.680
TO SANG YAN

17:58.240 --> 17:59.200
Sang Yan.

18:00.000 --> 18:01.280
I'm…

18:01.360 --> 18:04.200
I'm in no position to ask you to forgive
me for leaving without saying goodbye.

18:05.080 --> 18:07.600
It was like that last time,
and it's the same now.

18:09.160 --> 18:10.960
I don't expect you to understand me,

18:11.480 --> 18:12.720
but please believe

18:12.800 --> 18:14.880
that I have reasons why I must leave.

18:15.960 --> 18:18.000
Do not miss or look for me.

18:19.240 --> 18:20.760
I wish you peace and joy

18:20.840 --> 18:22.360
in your future life.

18:22.880 --> 18:23.880
Shuangjiang.

18:40.760 --> 18:41.760
Hello.

18:41.840 --> 18:44.520
The user you're calling
is temporarily unavailable.

18:46.280 --> 18:47.360
Hello.

18:47.440 --> 18:49.960
The user you're calling
is temporarily unavailable.

18:50.760 --> 18:51.840
Please try again later.

18:52.680 --> 18:53.680
Hello.

18:53.760 --> 18:56.360
The user you're calling
is temporarily unavailable.

19:01.800 --> 19:03.520
What is your relationship with Wen Yifan?

19:04.040 --> 19:04.960
Lovers.

19:05.040 --> 19:06.600
And before she left,

19:06.680 --> 19:08.480
did you have any heated arguments?

19:09.000 --> 19:10.040
No.

19:11.640 --> 19:13.560
And were there any disputes between you,

19:13.640 --> 19:16.840
such as relationship-related or financial?

19:16.920 --> 19:18.000
No.

19:18.080 --> 19:20.880
So she just left this letter
and disappeared?

19:22.880 --> 19:25.320
Can you try to contact her family?

19:25.400 --> 19:27.760
I don't have
their contact information, so…

19:29.680 --> 19:31.280
We'll try to contact her family for you.

19:32.280 --> 19:33.600
You can sit over there and wait.

19:33.680 --> 19:34.880
Over there. You can sit over there.

19:35.880 --> 19:36.800
Thank you.

19:47.080 --> 19:49.800
We just contacted Wen Yifan's mother,
Ms. Zhao Yuandong.

19:50.560 --> 19:51.840
She told us

19:51.920 --> 19:54.440
that firstly, she doesn't approve
of your relationship.

19:54.520 --> 19:57.200
Secondly, Wen Yifan
often disappears suddenly,

19:57.280 --> 19:58.880
and they've had fights lately,

19:58.960 --> 20:02.200
so she thinks this time,
Wen Yifan is throwing a tantrum.

20:10.000 --> 20:12.920
Isn't her mom anxious at all?

20:14.480 --> 20:17.280
Based on her tone, it seems like it is.

20:18.080 --> 20:19.160
We also learned

20:19.240 --> 20:21.120
that her father is deceased

20:21.200 --> 20:22.800
and that she has no siblings.

20:22.880 --> 20:23.920
To your knowledge,

20:24.000 --> 20:27.000
does Wen Yifan have any close relatives

20:27.080 --> 20:28.920
or friends or anything like that?

20:31.360 --> 20:33.880
She has a close friend,

20:34.760 --> 20:36.600
but she doesn't know
where Wen Yifan is either.

20:39.080 --> 20:42.040
In fact, we often see
this kind of situation.

20:42.120 --> 20:44.040
Young people like Wen Yifan

20:44.640 --> 20:46.080
may not have any attachments.

20:50.200 --> 20:51.200
How about this?

20:51.280 --> 20:52.720
Give me your contact information.

20:53.600 --> 20:56.040
We'll be in touch if we hear anything.

20:57.160 --> 20:58.680
Don't worry too much.

20:58.760 --> 21:00.160
She's an adult,

21:00.240 --> 21:01.960
so she has the right to stay or go.

21:05.920 --> 21:07.840
Can't you do
any more investigation for me?

21:07.920 --> 21:10.440
Based on the information you've given us,

21:10.520 --> 21:12.800
we don't know if she's in danger,

21:12.880 --> 21:14.200
so,

21:14.280 --> 21:17.480
we have no right
to invade a citizen's privacy.

21:17.560 --> 21:18.800
Please understand.

21:20.680 --> 21:21.800
Young man.

21:21.880 --> 21:25.440
For this kind of thing, I think,
you, a boy, should take it easy.

21:37.280 --> 21:39.280
Do you really have no attachments at all?

21:44.920 --> 21:45.880
Wen Yifan.

21:47.240 --> 21:48.680
Where are you?

21:54.680 --> 21:59.280
HONG KONG, CHINA

22:39.800 --> 22:40.640
Have a drink.

22:41.680 --> 22:42.560
No.

22:51.320 --> 22:52.640
Don't be anxious.

22:53.680 --> 22:56.560
Maybe she'll come back alone one day.

22:57.840 --> 23:00.560
Yes, one day.

23:01.240 --> 23:03.560
It could be four or five years from now.

23:06.360 --> 23:09.200
I don't believe
she'll never answer her phone.

23:31.960 --> 23:33.240
In fact, after all these years,

23:34.080 --> 23:36.800
we're not sure what she's been through.

23:37.400 --> 23:39.520
When I called the police,

23:40.400 --> 23:42.240
I suddenly realized
that she had no family.

23:43.560 --> 23:44.880
We are all her family.

23:48.760 --> 23:50.440
I hope she feels the same way.

23:50.960 --> 23:53.640
See what you want to eat.
There's some here

23:54.160 --> 23:55.720
and on the back.

23:55.800 --> 23:57.880
And there's something just made.

23:58.480 --> 23:59.640
In the back part, too.

23:59.720 --> 24:00.920
We just made it. What do you want?

24:02.800 --> 24:04.480
- No. 8.
- No. 8.

24:04.560 --> 24:06.000
Okay. No problem.

24:06.800 --> 24:08.000
No. 8.

24:08.080 --> 24:09.760
Maybe it's because

24:12.560 --> 24:14.200
I didn't make her trust me enough

24:16.480 --> 24:19.240
that she chose to suffer alone again.

24:27.360 --> 24:28.440
Su Haoan.

24:29.480 --> 24:30.880
Take a vacation for me tomorrow.

24:32.080 --> 24:33.240
I need time

24:34.080 --> 24:35.240
to find out.

24:49.920 --> 24:52.360
Hello. I just booked a room.

24:52.880 --> 24:54.000
Do you want to rent it for a long time?

24:55.320 --> 24:56.680
You have to pay the rent first.

24:57.400 --> 24:59.840
Wait a minute. Come and pay later.

25:00.400 --> 25:01.400
Here you go.

25:01.920 --> 25:02.840
Thank you.

25:05.200 --> 25:06.200
Okay.

25:55.360 --> 25:58.920
ZHIBAI VILLA

26:09.120 --> 26:12.280
Before, Dian lived
with her grandmother for a while.

26:12.920 --> 26:14.520
I remember I went there once.

26:16.840 --> 26:18.320
She adored my dad,

26:19.120 --> 26:20.560
so she adored me.

26:22.120 --> 26:23.320
That time

26:23.400 --> 26:25.800
was probably the happiest she'd been

26:25.880 --> 26:27.800
since her dad passed away.

26:30.080 --> 26:32.000
Two.

26:33.440 --> 26:34.360
Come on.

26:37.920 --> 26:39.080
It gets better.

26:45.240 --> 26:46.280
Supplemental tile of melding quad.

26:46.360 --> 26:47.760
Excuse me.

26:50.040 --> 26:50.920
Ma'am.

26:51.440 --> 26:54.400
Is this No.72, Haiyue Branch Road?

26:54.480 --> 26:55.440
Yes.

26:55.520 --> 26:57.720
Do you know Wen Yifan?

26:58.240 --> 27:01.040
I've lived here for seven or eight years,
but I've never heard of her.

27:02.240 --> 27:04.560
Have any strange girls come here recently?

27:04.640 --> 27:05.960
Not that I've seen.

27:07.440 --> 27:08.760
Thank you. Sorry to bother you.

27:14.800 --> 27:16.960
Could you have left Nanwu?

27:20.960 --> 27:25.400
YIHE UNIVERSITY

27:29.880 --> 27:31.560
Sang Yan?

27:31.640 --> 27:33.840
I'm Xu Xinxin, Wen Yifan's roommate.

27:33.920 --> 27:35.080
Sorry to bother you.

27:35.680 --> 27:38.000
Wen Yifan wasn't really
special in college,

27:38.080 --> 27:39.880
but she didn't talk much.

27:39.960 --> 27:42.280
When she was looking for a job,
she didn't seem to want

27:42.360 --> 27:43.440
to work in her hometown,

27:43.520 --> 27:45.600
so she did an internship at Yihe Daily.

27:46.120 --> 27:47.600
So, did she ever say

27:47.680 --> 27:48.800
why she didn't want
to go back to her hometown?

27:48.880 --> 27:50.280
Anyway, ever since she started college,

27:50.360 --> 27:52.680
she's applied to stay at school
during winter and summer vacations.

27:52.760 --> 27:54.240
We were kind of surprised,

27:54.320 --> 27:55.840
but she didn't explain.

27:59.880 --> 28:01.000
Thank you.

28:04.000 --> 28:06.080
And how is she working at Yihe Daily?

28:08.520 --> 28:09.920
To be honest, actually,

28:10.800 --> 28:13.960
we didn't have much contact
after the internship,

28:14.880 --> 28:17.400
so I don't really know

28:17.480 --> 28:19.000
what happened to her afterward.

28:21.120 --> 28:22.160
Thank you.

28:23.600 --> 28:24.800
Wen Yifan?

28:25.640 --> 28:26.480
I remember.

28:26.560 --> 28:28.680
She had such a personality,
so how could I not remember?

28:29.560 --> 28:31.480
So, what happened then?

28:32.440 --> 28:34.440
What's your relationship with Wen Yifan?

28:34.520 --> 28:35.600
Her boyfriend.

28:36.520 --> 28:37.720
All I can tell you is that someone

28:37.800 --> 28:39.640
sexually harassed her in the workplace
but didn't make it.

28:41.480 --> 28:44.560
The editorial director at the time
was fired because of it,

28:44.640 --> 28:45.960
and we did everything we could

28:46.040 --> 28:48.320
to get justice for her
to restore her reputation,

28:48.840 --> 28:50.560
but she wasn't happy about it

28:50.640 --> 28:51.720
and quit her job.

29:09.960 --> 29:11.120
Maybe she wanted to escape.

29:11.640 --> 29:12.960
Young people these days always escape

29:13.040 --> 29:14.480
when they are under pressure.

29:15.920 --> 29:17.040
What kind of escape is that?

29:18.560 --> 29:19.640
If Wen Yifan were your daughter,

29:20.680 --> 29:22.600
would you let her continue
to suffer from this kind of pressure?

29:28.680 --> 29:29.960
Please take that back.

29:40.120 --> 29:42.360
In Nanwu or Yihe,

29:43.040 --> 29:44.480
there is no sign of you

29:45.840 --> 29:47.480
or any answer.

29:52.240 --> 29:53.320
Now,

29:54.400 --> 29:56.240
there's only one last place left.

30:21.200 --> 30:22.440
Why are you back so late?

30:23.040 --> 30:24.720
I was at a place to study.

30:26.400 --> 30:28.400
What are you studying for?

30:29.040 --> 30:31.120
I think you were
just slacking off on purpose.

30:31.200 --> 30:33.760
There are so many people
waiting for dinner at home.

30:33.840 --> 30:35.720
Why couldn't you come back early to help?

30:36.240 --> 30:37.880
Oh my God.

30:37.960 --> 30:39.120
Are you fooling around

30:39.200 --> 30:41.320
with some punk again?

30:53.000 --> 30:54.520
I heard from my mom

30:56.640 --> 30:57.920
that Wen Yifan disappeared again.

31:01.280 --> 31:02.360
Why did you say "again"?

31:03.000 --> 31:05.400
I remember it was after
the College Entrance Exam.

31:07.240 --> 31:08.880
One day, she suddenly disappeared

31:09.720 --> 31:10.600
without taking anything.

31:11.200 --> 31:12.840
She never came back after that.

31:13.840 --> 31:14.680
What was the reason for that?

31:16.160 --> 31:19.040
She didn't tell you?

31:24.040 --> 31:26.360
I was preparing for my exams,

31:26.440 --> 31:27.320
so I didn't know anything.

31:27.400 --> 31:29.080
Ask someone else.

31:32.800 --> 31:34.400
So, when will your family come back?

31:35.240 --> 31:36.760
My mom and my uncle moved to Nanwu.

31:37.800 --> 31:38.960
Moved to Nanwu?

31:44.080 --> 31:45.080
Where do they live?

31:46.200 --> 31:49.720
I think you can just ask Wen Yifan's mom.

31:49.800 --> 31:50.960
I really don't know anything.

31:53.720 --> 31:54.760
Thanks.

32:02.440 --> 32:03.680
Can I see

32:03.760 --> 32:05.800
the room she used to live in?

32:09.320 --> 32:10.440
That's it.

32:11.720 --> 32:13.120
This used to be her room.

32:50.120 --> 32:51.040
I'm home.

32:51.800 --> 32:53.720
Are you going back to this shabby place?

32:53.800 --> 32:55.880
Have a seat. I'll go pack.

33:09.960 --> 33:11.280
Let me talk some more.

33:12.200 --> 33:13.280
Fan.

33:13.360 --> 33:14.560
Happy New Year.

33:14.640 --> 33:16.880
Come here if you're free.

33:17.880 --> 33:19.080
Right.

33:24.120 --> 33:26.120
Why are you so ignorant?

33:26.640 --> 33:28.720
Fan. Don't be so upset.

33:29.600 --> 33:30.520
Be strong.

33:48.320 --> 33:51.560
NOTES, SAMPLING METHODS, SAMPLE PRINCIPLES

33:56.280 --> 34:00.920
TARGET: NANWU UNIVERSITY!

34:02.160 --> 34:04.240
I'll come to you tomorrow.

34:04.320 --> 34:06.200
I'm going back to Nanwu soon.

34:06.280 --> 34:07.560
Don't come.

34:07.640 --> 34:08.679
When?

34:08.760 --> 34:10.040
When

34:10.120 --> 34:12.800
the acceptance letter is sent to me.

34:13.560 --> 34:14.880
TARGET: NANWU UNIVERSITY!

34:32.080 --> 34:35.199
BUILDING 7

34:41.960 --> 34:42.840
Zhong Siqiao.

34:42.920 --> 34:46.120
Last time you said that her mom
lives in Building 7, right?

34:53.639 --> 34:54.679
Thank you.

35:27.320 --> 35:28.400
Sang Yan.

35:28.480 --> 35:29.600
Sang Yan.

35:29.680 --> 35:30.880
I'm Fu Zhuang.

35:30.960 --> 35:32.240
It's really you.

35:32.840 --> 35:33.880
- Are you going to work?
- Yes.

35:34.560 --> 35:36.920
Yifan quit. You didn't know?

35:39.520 --> 35:42.400
Is she quitting because
something good will happen to you?

35:42.480 --> 35:43.600
Congratulate her for me.

35:45.440 --> 35:46.360
Fu Zhuang.

35:46.440 --> 35:48.000
When did that guy come here to work
as a security guard?

35:48.680 --> 35:49.640
That guy?

35:51.040 --> 35:53.560
He's been here
for almost a month. What's wrong?

35:55.360 --> 35:56.200
Nothing.

35:56.280 --> 35:57.280
Then I'll go to work.

35:57.360 --> 35:58.200
I'll be late.

35:58.280 --> 35:59.800
Tell Yifan we'll party soon.

35:59.880 --> 36:01.520
And congratulations.

36:05.520 --> 36:06.560
Take it back.

36:06.640 --> 36:12.320
EXPRESS DELIVERY

37:05.880 --> 37:07.080
Don't be sad.

37:11.360 --> 37:14.240
I understand if she didn't tell me
during the entrance exam.

37:14.320 --> 37:16.640
We were kids then, so she didn't trust me.

37:18.400 --> 37:20.720
But now, we've both grown up.

37:22.320 --> 37:24.600
Am I terribly unqualified
to be her friend?

37:27.960 --> 37:31.000
Actually, everyone has something

37:31.600 --> 37:33.920
they can't just say.

37:34.600 --> 37:36.080
We don't have to beat ourselves up.

37:38.800 --> 37:41.000
I just want to help her.

37:41.080 --> 37:42.800
She's alone again now.

37:42.880 --> 37:44.440
How lonely will she be?

37:55.080 --> 37:56.320
DIAN: QIAO, IS IT CONVENIENT TO TALK?

37:57.800 --> 38:00.400
IT EXTREMELY IS!

38:02.520 --> 38:03.480
Hello?

38:03.560 --> 38:04.520
Hello, Qiao.

38:05.040 --> 38:06.960
Dian, where are you?

38:07.960 --> 38:09.720
We've been looking all over for you.

38:10.280 --> 38:12.520
I'm sorry to have worried you.

38:13.320 --> 38:14.960
What's going on?

38:18.640 --> 38:20.480
Are you never going to come back?

38:21.480 --> 38:22.720
When you left me,

38:22.800 --> 38:25.240
it took me a long time to adjust.

38:27.440 --> 38:29.360
Then I worked very hard

38:29.440 --> 38:32.400
and kept myself busy,
so I wouldn't feel so lonely.

38:35.320 --> 38:38.760
You have to think
about Sang Yan, if not me.

38:38.840 --> 38:40.680
You've just fallen in love.

38:41.720 --> 38:42.800
Is he alright?

38:43.480 --> 38:44.440
No.

38:46.680 --> 38:49.360
Didn't you say he was always so bright

38:50.040 --> 38:51.680
and energetic?

38:53.440 --> 38:56.120
But now, he isn't bright at all.

38:58.520 --> 38:59.840
Tell me where you are.

39:00.480 --> 39:02.240
He's going crazy looking for you.

39:04.000 --> 39:05.200
I'm sorry.

39:05.280 --> 39:08.360
Dian, I'm begging you. Come back.

39:08.440 --> 39:09.360
Qiao.

39:09.960 --> 39:12.720
I'm calling you to tell you I'm safe.

39:13.360 --> 39:14.720
Don't worry about me.

39:19.000 --> 39:20.880
I didn't want to leave
without saying goodbye.

39:23.200 --> 39:25.000
I just want you all to be okay.

39:27.280 --> 39:28.960
I left not because I didn't love you.

39:33.360 --> 39:34.760
- Dian.
- Take care.

40:17.440 --> 40:21.920
THE STORY IS NOT OVER YET…

40:22.680 --> 40:23.880
Would you like to order something else?

40:24.480 --> 40:25.880
No, thank you.

41:07.080 --> 41:08.680
BAI JIANG

41:09.760 --> 41:11.120
OUR RABBIT IS STARVING TO BE VERY THIN

41:11.200 --> 41:12.800
THE FLOWERS IN OUR GARDEN ARE WILTING

41:12.880 --> 41:14.400
WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN?

41:23.640 --> 41:25.600
I WANT TO DISSOLVE THE RELATIONSHIP

41:25.680 --> 41:27.000
WE AGREED TO DISSOLVE OUR RELATIONSHIP
I'LL DISSOLVE OUR RELATIONSHIP BY FORCE

41:30.040 --> 41:36.720
WE AGREED TO DISSOLVE OUR RELATIONSHIP.
I'LL DISSOLVE OUR RELATIONSHIP BY FORCE

44:43.080 --> 44:44.240
HUGE THANKS TO EVERYONE INVOLVED
AND TO ALL THE FANS OF THE FIRST FROST!

44:44.320 --> 44:45.480
TREAT YOURSELF WELL
AND THE WORLD WILL HOLD MORE LOVE FOR YOU!
